{"word":"G1769 - ἐννεός - enneós - en-neh-os' - Speechless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐννεός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enneós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-neh-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Speechless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரமித்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"speechless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1770 - ἐννεύω - enneúō - en-nyoo'-o/1770\">G1770</a>; <i>dumb</i> (as <i>making signs</i>), that is, <i>silent</i> from astonishment: - speechless.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}